Android exam tasks

1. Create a new button in the MainActivity. If pressed write out a short text onto the screen in a Toast.
2. Create a new activity and start it with the previous button.
3. Create an EditText field on the MainActivity and pass the given text to your new activity (show this text on the new activity).
4. Create a Service and start it when you start your new activity. Create az EditText field and a Button here and print the given text in a Toast from the Service class.